{"id":251049,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/09/维权网-上海民众到市政府集会抗议对冯正虎等人/","date":"2012-09-11T05:31:17Z","modified":"2012-09-11T05:31:17Z","title":"维权网 | 上海民众到市政府集会抗议对冯正虎等人的非法关押（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员晨晓报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日</span><span>下午</span><span>，上海部分维权民众自发聚集在上海市人民大道</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span>号，市委、市政府、市人大信访办门前抗议上海当局非法限制公民人身自由：声援冯正虎、朱金娣、崔福芳等人被关黑监狱。后来得知被上海政府迫害关押黑监狱的维权者还有顾永洪。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>冯正虎多年来义务做推进法治维护人权的工作，帮助访民依法维权，维护法律的尊严和权威，批评与揭露上海政府的腐败，揭露与批评上海法院侵犯公民诉权的司法不作为现象，并倡导维护公民诉权的活动：“我要立案，捍卫法律，还我诉权”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>冯正虎等上海公民依法向各级法院提起行政诉讼，《民事诉讼法》第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">112</span><span>条，《行政诉讼法》第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">42</span><span>条规定，应当在七日内立案或者作出裁定不受理。法院超过法定的立案受理期限，即不立案又不裁定，这就是司法不作为，即非法剥夺公民诉权。这种公然践踏法律和司法无赖行为，在中国的地方法院非常普遍，成了阻碍司法公正的绊脚石。这么简单程序的法律规定，法院都可以不遵守，还能坚守审判中的司法公正吗？而且，公民诉权的丧失，这就意味着公民的所有合法权益得不到国家法律保护。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>因此，冯正虎成了上海当局的“眼中钉、肉中刺”，从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日</span><span>被关押在政通路</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">240</span><span>弄</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">302</span><span>室家庭监狱至今已</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">198</span><span>天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>崔福芳被囚禁在浦东新区金扬街道德平路</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1189</span><span>弄</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>号达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>天；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>日</span><span>下午，朱金娣在北京最高人民法院正常上访时，遭到上海浦东新区地方政府派遣到北京截访的保安人员绑架。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日</span><span>晚上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>时多钟，朱金娣被押回上海，关押在地方政府私自设立在上海市浦东大道</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2900</span><span>号金华旅馆</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">103</span><span>房间的黑监狱内。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日</span><span>至今，朱金娣与外界失去联系，现下落不明，生死未卜。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>顾永洪</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日</span><span>在虹桥火车站被截访人员关进黑监狱至今未释放。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>因此，上海民众强烈要求上海市政府立即释放被非法拘禁的维权人士冯正虎、朱金娣、崔福芳、顾永洪等维权人士，依法保障公民人身自由的权利。</span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-_YxuABlTa1w/UE6enQ2m4aI/AAAAAAAAN4I/2gUSUby11wM/s1600/DSCI1096.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"202\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-_YxuABlTa1w/UE6enQ2m4aI/AAAAAAAAN4I/2gUSUby11wM/s320/DSCI1096.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>民众抗议上海当局非法限制公民人身自由，声援冯正虎朱金娣崔福芳等人被关黑见监狱</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Sm2dqMJDYV8/UE6eplmynVI/AAAAAAAAN4Q/bgGqTaUFBNw/s1600/%E6%B0%91%E4%BC%97%E6%8A%97%E8%AE%AE%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E5%BD%93%E5%B1%80%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E4%BA%BA%E8%BA%AB%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%EF%BC%8C%E5%A3%B0%E6%8F%B4%E5%86%AF%E6%AD%A3%E8%99%8E%E6%9C%B1%E9%87%91%E5%A8%A3%E5%B4%94%E7%A6%8F%E8%8A%B3%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E5%85%B3%E9%BB%91%E8%A7%81%E7%9B%91%E7%8B%B1.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"195\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Sm2dqMJDYV8/UE6eplmynVI/AAAAAAAAN4Q/bgGqTaUFBNw/s320/%E6%B0%91%E4%BC%97%E6%8A%97%E8%AE%AE%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E5%BD%93%E5%B1%80%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E4%BA%BA%E8%BA%AB%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%EF%BC%8C%E5%A3%B0%E6%8F%B4%E5%86%AF%E6%AD%A3%E8%99%8E%E6%9C%B1%E9%87%91%E5%A8%A3%E5%B4%94%E7%A6%8F%E8%8A%B3%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E5%85%B3%E9%BB%91%E8%A7%81%E7%9B%91%E7%8B%B1.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-6638200146371785789?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}